column5: <literal xml:lang='tok'>ma seme li lawa e ijo ni</literal>
<literal xml:lang='tok'>ona li kama sona tan jan seme</literal>
<literal xml:lang='tok'>ijo li ona la ijo li seme kin</literal>
<literal xml:lang='tok'>li jo e ijo pi kulupu ni</literal>
<literal xml:lang='tok'>lipu ni li toki e ijo ni</literal>
<literal xml:lang='tok'>ma lili li lon ma ni</literal>
<literal xml:lang='tok'>nanpa la ma ona pi open suno li lon seme</literal>
<literal xml:lang='tok'>nanpa lon nasin lipu pi ma Tosi</literal>
<literal xml:lang='tok'>nasin mute pi ijo ni li tan seme</literal>
<literal xml:lang='tok'>ni li lon ma lawa seme</literal>
<literal xml:lang='tok'>ona li kama lon ma seme</literal>
<literal xml:lang='tok'>ona li ma tomo lawa pi ma seme</literal>
<literal xml:lang='tok'>ona li mama pi jan pi mute seme</literal>
<literal xml:lang='tok'>ijo lili pi suli nanpa wan</literal>
<literal xml:lang='tok'>ijo suli pi lili nanpa wan</literal>
<literal xml:lang='tok'>ona li lon kulupu seme pi tenpo ilo</literal>
<literal xml:lang='tok'>nanpa la ona li lon seme</literal>
<literal xml:lang='tok'>nimi "ona" ona li seme lon toki ante</literal>
<literal xml:lang='tok'>ona li ante ale tawa ijo ni</literal>
<literal xml:lang='tok'>ona li jo e sijelo lon lipu ilo seme</literal>
<literal xml:lang='tok'>ona li kama lon tenpo seme</literal>
<literal xml:lang='tok'>ona li ken sama ijo ni</literal>
<literal xml:lang='tok'>pali musi sijelo la kulupu seme li pona tawa ona</literal>
<literal xml:lang='tok'>seme la jan li kama sona e nasin pona</literal>
<literal xml:lang='tok'>lawa jo pi pali ona la</literal>
<literal xml:lang='tok'>lipu ni li toki e ni</literal>
<literal xml:lang='tok'>ni li tawa nasin kule seme</literal>
<literal xml:lang='tok'>ona li pana e sona tawa jan seme</literal>
